title: 18 in. Steel Handle Polypropylene Blade Ergonomic Snow Shovel
description: This outdoor pusher/shovel combo blade makes it easy to both push and lift snow to more evenly and easily clear out a walkway, driveway or patio. Plus, the angle of the shovel blade or handle can be adjusted to suit every person's needs. The shovel features a powder-coated steel handle with a D-shaped polypropylene grip as well as a polypropylene shovel with metal scraper blade.
